<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ລະບົບໂຄສະນາເລື່ອນ</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Lao&display=swap">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Lao:wght@400;700&display=swap">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Lao:wght@400;700&display=swap">
</head>

<body>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans Lao', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;

        }

        .promo-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1f99a6, #21565e);
            color: #f4f4f4;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 14px 0;
            white-space: nowrap;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .promo-text {
            display: inline-block;
            padding-left: 100%;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700px;
            animation: marquee-animation 20s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes marquee-animation {
            0% {
                transform: translateX(0);
            }

            100% {
                transform: translateX(-100%);
            }
        }

        .promo-wrapper:hover .promo-text {
            animation-play-state: paused;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #085179;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #085179;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #23989c;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .spacer {
            height: 1000px;
        }
    </style>

    <div class="promo-wrapper">
        <div class="promo-text">BCSP4A-AM ສນ ກໍລະກັນ ຮຽວທະວີສຸກ</div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>ລະບົບໂຄສະນາເລື່ອນ</h1>
        <p>ສ້າງການໂຄສະນາແບບເລື່ອນໃນເວັບໄຊ ເພາະໃນເວັບໄຊ ການໂຄສະນາແບບເລື່ອນ ແນ່ນ ການໂຄສະນາແບບເລື່ອນ  </p>
        <a href="https://web.whatsapp.com" class="cta-button">ເບີ່ງສີນຄ້າ</a>
        <div class="spacer"></div>

</body>


</html>